us, unmitigated gap (A\u2019s unknown reliability/stress, B\u2019s toxic communication, D\u2019s missing technical competence and poor leadership).\u202fTherefore, I support **Candidate\u202fC** as the best overall fit.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
